channel.title: Exercises: Objects and Math :: Introduction to Web Dev
channel.description: At our space base, it is a historic day! Five non-human animals are ready to run a space mission without our assistance! For the exercises, you will use the same five animal objects throughout. Open up ObjectExercises.js in javascript-projects/objects-and-math/exercises to find all the starter code you will need for these exercises. Part 1: Create More Objects Based on the two object literals provided in the starter code, create new object literals for three more animals:
